description: Listed building consent for the erection of a replacement welcome cabin at the entrance of the car park, a cycle hire cabin by the cycle skills area, and a timber clad shipping container in the car park to be used as storage.
decision_conditions: Condition : 1 - The works to which this consent relates, must be begun not later than the expiration of three years beginning with the date of this consent.

Condition : 2 - The development hereby permitted shall be carried out in accordance with the following approved plans and specifications: OST1/01, Unnumbered Location Plan, Unnumbered Site Plan, Unnumbered Site Block Plan, Heritage Statement, Unnumbered Proposed Plans and Elevations, Received 08 September 2023
